result.name: Royal's Pub

reviews.text: Great vibe. Very friendly and Accommodating staff.

Exactly what I was looking for, a place to sit at the bar, sip over a delicious imported beer, regular music and good ambient. The waitresses are nice and you don't feel rushed. They have good dinner options for just 80HKD but I had already ate so I don't know about the quality. Beer goes from 50-80, snacks 40-70 and main dishes from 70-130. I will definitely come back and try the dinner options. They have happy hour with discount average of 10-20 on drinks. Enjoy
Nice place for a drink but the food is lousy
Small but good atmosphere and menu.

Been there 3 times:
1- for lunch menu and for the price (70$)  food was ok
2- for drinks at night and the staff was so rude with us.
3- for dinner set: food was really average for the price you payed (140$)!! 

> don’t think i will ever go back.
